Which game? Are you trying to edit 8x16 pixel sprites? Otherwise, how do you expect a generic tile editor to know which order the game program uses the tiles in? It appears you want a tile editor that runs within an emulator, and this is about the <em>only</em> reason I'd use nesticle nowadays.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=9">tepples</a> — Wed Dec 08, 2004 10:07 am</p><hr />
